N₀ ≈ 10⁵ × 10¹⁸ × 10⁷ ≈ 10⁴⁰

(10⁵ zones × 10¹⁸ events per day × approximately 10⁷ days of active operation, equivalently representing the effective attempt window over 4.5 billion years).

Even if the probability that a single random molecular cluster happens to possess the most primitive autocatalytic or semipermeable membrane boundary function is as low as 10⁻²⁵, with 10⁴⁰ independent attempts:

